  ('social-worker-moex-02525', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者屬於「古典管理觀點」中的代表人物？', '["彼得杜拉克（Peter Drucker）", "道格拉斯麥格雷特（Douglas McGregor）", "亨利費堯（Henri Fayol）", "威廉戴明（Willam E. Deming）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02526', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據羅伯卡茲（Robert Katz）的說法，成功的管理者應具備的基本管理技巧（或技能），包括下列那三個 面向？', '["概念、技術、人際關係", "抽象、具體、公共關係", "設計、執行、評估", "行銷、財務、資訊"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02527', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據管理學者道格拉斯麥格雷特（Douglas McGregor）的主張，下列何者不是Y理論所強調的重點？', '["組織的需求應該重於個人的需求", "組織應辦理自我評核管理", "組織應實施參與管理及諮商", "組織強調分權與授權"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7528bca53179", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6a2111ca5bab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104030", "c": "110", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
